ike":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T17:43:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c6ab8622c5519e8b177fdb0e6a0350d674768350","tid":1115981,"uid":19725,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"8851d218bf76f549cfa108e0645b4af9da0a0b6f","tid":1115981,"uid":73200,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"52e58e98f02fa1ece45fb17f17ebce5c2333aef3","tid":1115981,"uid":83228,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T17:41:59.000Z","msg":"好多打手想spin到大陸醫生來港<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />港"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T17:43:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T18:16:05.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">強烈要求引入中國醫生</span> </span></strong><br />\n五千年黎中國偉大文化 一定要入引中國醫生解決香港班仆街醫生<br />\n好撚唔抵得佢地咁高人工，一定要拉到佢1萬5千蚊一個月 低過洗碗阿姐！！！！！！ 大家一齊跟我大字報<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n孕婦剖腹產子被偷腎 中國新華醫院院長供認曾偷九個腎<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20120829/18002608\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20120829%2F18002608&d=7%2FYu9khx8AV6Haip52opSfDXWQKahOldmH8%2Bpia8yKE%3D&h=b48ed19b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20120829%2F18002608&h=24a56f2c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20120829/18002608</a><br />\n<br />\n手術後腎消失 農婦尋腎3年無果<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ntdtv.com/b5/2015/01/29/a1172952.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ntdtv.com%2Fb5%2F2015%2F01%2F29%2Fa1172952.html&d=7%2FYu9khx8AV6Haip52opSfDXWQKahOldmH8%2Bpia8yKE%3D&h=e6a71fec\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ntdtv.com/b5/2015/01/29/a1172952.html</a><br />\n<br />\n包皮手術割一半醫生停下加價1萬5！ 病人負傷起來繳費<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/882584-中國-包皮手術割一半醫生停下加價1萬5！+病人負傷起來繳費\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F882584-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-%E5%8C%85%E7%9A%AE%E6%89%8B%E8%A1%93%E5%89%B2%E4%B8%80%E5%8D%8A%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F%E5%81%9C%E4%B8%8B%E5%8A%A0%E5%83%B91%E8%90%AC5%EF%BC%81%2B%E7%97%85%E4%BA%BA%E8%B2%A0%E5%82%B7%E8%B5%B7%E4%BE%86%E7%B9%B3%E8%B2%BB&d=7%2FYu9khx8AV6Haip52opSfDXWQKahOldmH8%2Bpia8yKE%3D&h=ce4e72a3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F882584-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-%E5%8C%85%E7%9A%AE%E6%89%8B%E8%A1%93%E5%89%B2%E4%B8%80%E5%8D%8A%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F%E5%81%9C%E4%B8%8B%E5%8A%A0%E5%83%B91%E8%90%AC5%EF%BC%81%2B%E7%97%85%E4%BA%BA%E8%B2%A0%E5%82%B7%E8%B5%B7%E4%BE%86%E7%B9%B3%E8%B2%BB&h=c41842b2\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/882584-中國-包皮手術割一半醫生停下加價1萬5！+病人負傷起來繳費</a><br />\n<br />\n重慶醫生手術途中突加碼 費用飆升13倍<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20151130/bkncn-20151130041046031-1130_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20151130%2Fbkncn-20151130041046031-1130_05011_001.html&d=7%2FYu9khx8AV6Haip52opSfDXWQKahOldmH8%2Bpia8yKE%3D&h=c7225d6b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20151130/bkncn-20151130041046031-1130_05011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n江蘇男割包皮 醫生手術中加價5倍 院方：沒違規 <br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/兩岸/article/20181205/s00004/1543977455217/江蘇男割包皮-醫生手術中加價5倍-院方-沒違規\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%85%A9%E5%B2%B8%2Farticle%2F20181205%2Fs00004%2F1543977455217%2F%E6%B1%9F%E8%98%87%E7%94%B7%E5%89%B2%E5%8C%85%E7%9A%AE-%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F%E6%89%8B%E8%A1%93%E4%B8%AD%E5%8A%A0%E5%83%B95%E5%80%8D-%E9%99%A2%E6%96%B9-%E6%B2%92%E9%81%95%E8%A6%8F&d=7%2FYu9khx8AV6Haip52opSfDXWQKahOldmH8%2Bpia8yKE%3D&h=59e8a99d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%85%A9%E5%B2%B8%2Farticle%2F20181205%2Fs00004%2F1543977455217%2F%E6%B1%9F%E8%98%87%E7%94%B7%E5%89%B2%E5%8C%85%E7%9A%AE-%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F%E6%89%8B%E8%A1%93%E4%B8%AD%E5%8A%A0%E5%83%B95%E5%80%8D-%E9%99%A2%E6%96%B9-%E6%B2%92%E9%81%95%E8%A6%8F&h=3aa50e06\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/兩岸/article/20181205/s00004/1543977455217/江蘇男割包皮-醫生手術中加價5倍-院方-沒違規</a><br />\n<br />\n成都女子手術麻醉後竟被醫生強姦 警方：嫌犯現已被捕<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/即時中國/191422/成都女子手術麻醉後竟被醫生強姦-警方-嫌犯現已被捕\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%2F191422%2F%E6%88%90%E9%83%BD%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%90%E6%89%8B%E8%A1%93%E9%BA%BB%E9%86%89%E5%BE%8C%E7%AB%9F%E8%A2%AB%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F%E5%BC%B7%E5%A7%A6-%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9-%E5%AB%8C%E7%8A%AF%E7%8F%BE%E5%B7%B2%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95&d=7%2FYu9khx8AV6Haip52opSfDXWQKahOldmH8%2Bpia8yKE%3D&h=314a413d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/即時中國/191422/成都女子手術麻醉後竟被醫生強姦-警方-嫌犯現已被捕</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/大國小事/288428/成都無牌醫生將女患者麻醉後強姦-多項罪成獲刑6年4個月\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E5%A4%A7%E5%9C%8B%E5%B0%8F%E4%BA%8B%2F288428%2F%E6%88%90%E9%83%BD%E7%84%A1%E7%89%8C%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F%E5%B0%87%E5%A5%B3%E6%82%A3%E8%80%85%E9%BA%BB%E9%86%89%E5%BE%8C%E5%BC%B7%E5%A7%A6-%E5%A4%9A%E9%A0%85%E7%BD%AA%E6%88%90%E7%8D%B2%E5%88%916%E5%B9%B44%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88&d=7%2FYu9khx8AV6Haip52opSfDXWQKahOldmH8%2Bpia8yKE%3D&h=5f37e113\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/大國小事/288428/成都無牌醫生將女患者麻醉後強姦-多項罪成獲刑6年4個月</a><br />\n<br />\n辦案人員經查發現，羅平沒有取得醫師資格證和醫師執業證。他於2017年6月開始在雙流區某街道開設的「1+1服務中心」從事醫療活動，並辦理虛假的醫師資格證、醫師執業證和身份證，向雙流區某醫院提交。他又於2016年至2018年期間，階段性在雙流某醫院坐診。<br />\n<br />\n台灣婦產淫醫性侵病患<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20190222/1521664/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20190222%2F1521664%2F&d=7%2FYu9khx8AV6Haip52opSfDXWQKahOldmH8%2Bpia8yKE%3D&h=33c771ba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20190222%2F1521664%2F&h=6ef73b72\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20190222/1521664/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">強姦、偷腎、加價 、假醫生，少不免 沒事兒</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/re0xvoV.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fre0xvoV.gif&h=9fbdef6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">強國黨媒展視中國式CPR 救助心臟停頓病人<br />\n－＞未來香港將會獲得優秀中國式醫療！<br />\n</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZUF5Qo9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZUF5Qo9.jpg&h=7dca3fa7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">建議香港政府先提出引入英國醫生 <br />\n然後再偷偷地引入大陸醫生<br />\n咁樣就可以拉低醫生人工<br />\n我最想見到既事情先會發生！！！<br />\n我要佢地死、低人工過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ！</span><br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n自2012年起，醫管局以有限度註冊聘請了39名海外醫生來港執業，但截至2018年底只有10名仍在公立醫院服務，「事實是醫管局無法挽留本港的畢業醫生，也無法挽留海外畢業的醫生。」<br />\n<br />\n林晢玄早前接受訪問時指，可參考新加坡模式，讓指定院校名單的海外醫生免試到本港公立醫院工作，年期不限。有關建議可謂是「改良版」的有限度註冊制度。<br />\n<br />\n而公共醫療醫生協會今日（30日）再發表聲明，指歡迎任何擁有與本港同等專業資格的海外畢業醫生，遵從現有機制，且透過有限度註冊來港，但需確保海外醫生長期留在公立醫院。<br />\n<br />\n香港公共醫療醫生協會稱，政府在2003年沙士削減2667張病床、推俗稱「肥雞餐」的自願離職計劃、關閉護士學校、削減醫科學額，緊縮醫療開資，而這些措施的惡果終在十多年後出現。協會指香港公營醫療體系早就超出負荷，而醫院的工作環境已達不安全水平，嚴重危害病人安全及影響服務質素，而前線醫護仍一直努力工作，「哀我同業，咫尺但愁雷雨至，向來悲傷何其多？」<br />\n<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">以香港戰地環境引入高質英國醫生！<br />\n可能外國鬼佬鍾意戰地環境同埋語言挑戰</span></strong></span><br />\n大中華呢3個字已經夠吸引佢地<br />\n<br />\n睇下佢地NHS d醫院 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DJYOBJo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDJYOBJo.jpg&h=b6235a18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OrxvP3q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOrxvP3q.jpg&h=62b8bafb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4knr7P6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4knr7P6.jpg&h=d20ccc63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b60UxgO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb60UxgO.jpg&h=af70738c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MYP95BR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMYP95BR.jpg&h=2b03b738&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋我地香港d醫院<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SQWHGas.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSQWHGas.jpg&h=eb01e00e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qyJGcg9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqyJGcg9.jpg&h=a2c8d832&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4xsLDXa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4xsLDXa.jpg&h=ca2fec23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Skczxhm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSkczxhm.jpg&h=ed64d856&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Tjeexhq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTjeexhq.jpg&h=ac181a9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">英聯邦高質醫生一定好鍾意挑戰自己 快d邀請佢地黎香港做野</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"a5ec8a7603e3e9626f73b9008e37c43e0d5c4cb3","tid":1115981,"uid":35581,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8851d218bf76f549cfa108e0645b4af9da0a0b6f","tid":1115981,"uid":73200,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"52e58e98f02fa1ece45fb17f17ebce5c2333aef3","tid":1115981,"uid":83228,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T17:41:59.000Z","msg":"好多打手想spin到大陸醫生來港<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />港"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T17: